Relevance Scores

Previoously based on 
         TF/IDF
 Term Frequency/Inverse Document Frequency


 Currently using 
       Okapi BM25



 Term Frequency : How many time does the term apperar in the field for a given Document
 Inverse Document Frequency : HOw often does the term appear within the index
 Field-length norm : How long is the field ?


 BM25 :
   Better at handling stop word
   NonLinear Term Frequency Saturation
   Can be configured with parameters
   


  
